{
  "texts": [
    "With continued advancements in LLM capability, it is crucial for researchers, developers, and users to understand their inner workings.",
    "The future discovery of more efficient architectures, the development of dedicated neural network microchips, and the emergence of AI models that can train even more powerful AI models will lead to ever-scaling advancements.",
    "Neuro-symbolic computing promises to give AI chatbots accurate world knowledge by combining them with symbolic rule-based engines (Garcez and Lamb 2023).",
    "Hence, fostering a broader understanding of LLMs will contribute to responsible innovation and informed discussions on their potential impact on society, ensuring that humans harness the technology for greater good while eliminating unintended negative consequences.",
    "Readers at the time of this writing will remember using a deck of \"punch cards\" to program computers through the 1980s."
  ]
}